said at one point he saw combe trying to calm mirecki down and run 
through the drill with him mirecki then successfully accomplished 
the escape and towed combe he said 
but after that exercise breeden testified he saw both mirecki 
and combe go under and then combe surface towing mirecki breeden 
said he didnt actually see mirecki being forced back in but felt 
mirecki was clearly panicked and would not possibly have returned 
voluntarily 
