manslaughter and conspiracy to commit battery they are blevins 
combe petty officer 1st class david j smith petty officers 2nd 
class frankie d deaton and john w zelenock 
torchia the schools commanding officer is charged with 
dereliction of duty 
when the hearing ends dalesio will make a nonbinding 
recommendation to rear adm david r morris chief of naval air 
